## Proposed Changes

### Phase 1 — Database & Infrastructure

#### [NEW] `supabase/migrations/20260605000000_quiz_attempts.sql`
New table to track quiz attempts so students can see their history and teachers can see class performance:
```sql
quiz_attempts (
  id UUID PK,
  quiz_id UUID FK → quizzes,
  user_id UUID FK → auth.users (nullable for anonymous),
  answers_json JSONB,
  score INTEGER,
  total INTEGER,
  completed_at TIMESTAMPTZ
)
```
With RLS: students see own attempts, teachers see all.

#### [MODIFY] [middleware.ts](file:///c:/Users/MACANS/Desktop/Codes/medlearn-next/src/middleware.ts)
Create Next.js middleware at the `src/` level to protect:
- `/dashboard` → requires auth + `student` role
- `/teacher/*` → requires auth + `teacher`/`admin` role
- `/admin/*` → requires auth + `admin`/`teacher` role (already handled by layout, but middleware adds edge protection)

